{"tid":653829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[靈異]垃圾袋藏屍：發現屍體工人不適　工友拜祭求安心","createTime":"2018-05-05T05:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T07:03:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f587c5a9ec982a2e7937ac28fb853fdde57e86c5","tid":653829,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"東涌港珠澳大橋地盤，昨日揭發垃圾袋藏屍案。今晨8時許，工人如常開工，約10名工友為求安心，帶同香燭、燒肉、生果及汽水等，在現場合十鞠躬拜祭。據悉，揭發垃圾袋藏屍的工友，今日身體不適沒有上班，可能因昨日「嚇親」所致。另外，有工人對於地盤發生膠袋藏屍案指「唔驚」，因自己無做虧心事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180505/bkn-20180505122921057-0505_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180505%2Fbkn-20180505122921057-0505_00822_001.html&d=FEX5tlkpPGC2vXGalhBCLJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=1634e196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180505/bkn-20180505122921057-0505_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7d4cde0e8b5d1e96a0bebfca7b689c947e80e572","tid":653829,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180505/photo/bkn-20180505122921057-0505_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180505125026\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180505122921057-0505_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180505125026&h=9aad3716&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58bd0ec61c0f362ab6beb8c5c3ed1d14361504a8","tid":653829,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"返工=？"},{"pid":"db9eeeecd1e092d09945d2252d46ec6fd57bf10b","tid":653829,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bd0ec61c0f362ab6beb8c5c3ed1d14361504a8","tid":653829,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"返工=？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"ghost"}]}